   In other matches, fifth-seeded Justine Henin, coming off a victory
at the German Open, beat Francesca Schiavone, 7-6 (5), 6-2;
seventh-seeded Amelie Mauresmo defeated Nathalie Dechy, 6-1, 7-5;
Mary Pierce beat 13th-seeded Patty Schnyder, 6-3, 1-6, 6-2 and
16th-seeded Tatiana Panova advanced when Henrieta Nagyova retired
because of a thigh injury while trailing, 6-0, 5-2.

DOC.CX:
   Candlestick Park--Candlestick Park in San Francisco is 42 years old;
the 49ers have played there for 32 years. The age of the stadium was
incorrect in a Sports story Thursday.
